No. 10M51. Farhi Saeed Bin Mohammed, et al., Petitioners v. Barack H. Obama, President of the United States, et al. 562 U.S. 1090, 131 S. Ct. 811, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 9489.

178 L. Ed. 2d 529,

December 6, 2010.

Motion for leave to file a petition for writ of certiorari under seal granted.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion.
